'''Morrie Mullins''' was the Campaign Designer and Plot Director for the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|Living Force]] [[RPGA]] campaign for the [[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]] at the campaign's beginning. He co-wrote the ''[[Living Force Campaign Guide]]'' with [[Robert Wiese]], but for contractual reasons did not receive authorship credit. He wrote many adventures and online supplements for the campaign. He eventually stopped being the Plot Director, but continued to write many Living Force adventures and all the adventure supplements. (Other supplements which were not associated with specific adventures were rules updates written by [[August Hahn|August]] and [[Cynthia Hahn]].) He also wrote several of the the [[Planet Hoppers]] series of articles, which were eventually taken over by [[Cory J. Herndon]].

Morrie Mullins was the author of the following adventures or articles:
*[[Eye of the Sun trilogy]]
**''[[A Cularin Presence]]''
**''[[The Resistance Within]]''
**''[[A Revelation]]''
*[[Between the Worlds trilogy]]
**''[[TopWorld]]''
**''[[MidWorld]]''
**''[[UnderWorld]]''
*[[Clouds of Genarius trilogy]]
**''[[Clouded Paths]]'' {{C|Co-written with [[Jason Nichols]]}}
**''[[Into the Storm Clouds]]'' {{C|Co-written with Jason Nichols}}
